  <chapter>
    <title>Change History</title>

    <para>This section provides information on updates made in the document
    over various versions.<informaltable role="TEXT">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="2.0*"/>

          <colspec colname="c3" colwidth="6.0*"/>

          <thead>
            <row>
              <entry valign="top">
                <para role="TEXT">Version</para>
              </entry>

              <entry valign="top">
                <para role="TEXT">Description</para>
              </entry>
            </row>
          </thead>

          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry valign="top">
                <para role="TEXT">
                  <guilabel moreinfo="none">6.0</guilabel>
                </para>
              </entry>

              <entry valign="top">
                <para role="TEXT">This is the initial version of the
                document.</para>
              </entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry morerows="1" valign="top">
                <para role="TEXT">
                  <guilabel moreinfo="none">6.0.1.0</guilabel>
                </para>
              </entry>

              <entry valign="top">
                <para role="TEXT">The following products are added to the
                portfolio of trade products that offer new user
                experience:<itemizedlist>
                    <listitem>
                      <para>
                        <ulink url="FCC_modern_trade_client_en.Issued_undertaking.xml">
                          <xref linkend="UI_UX"/>
                        </ulink>
                      </para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                      <para>
                        <ulink url="FCC_modern_trade_client_en.received_undertaking.xml">
                          <xref linkend="RU_UX"/>
                        </ulink>
                      </para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                      <para>
                        <ulink url="FCC_modern_trade_client_en.issued_slc.xml">
                          <xref linkend="SI_UX"/>
                        </ulink>
                      </para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                      <para>
                        <ulink url="FCC_modern_trade_client_en.received_slc.xml">
                          <xref linkend="SR_UX"/>
                        </ulink>
                      </para>
                    </listitem>
                  </itemizedlist></para>
              </entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="top">
                <para role="TEXT">The<ulink
                    url="FCC_modern_trade_client_en.collab_suite.xml">
                    <xref linkend="CollaborationSuite"/>
                  </ulink>, which provides a communication channel between
                different actors of international trade operations, is
                introduced in all the trade products.</para>
              </entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry morerows="3" valign="top">
                <para role="TEXT">
                  <guilabel moreinfo="none">6.0.2.0</guilabel>
                </para>
              </entry>

              <entry valign="top">
                <para role="TEXT">The <xi:include href="../entities_en.xml"
                xpointer="ent_Issued_LOI"
                xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"/>, product is moved
                into new angular framework with enhanced user experience.
                Refer<ulink url="FCC_modern_trade_client_en.indemnity.xml">
                    <xref linkend="LI_UX"/>
                  </ulink> for detailed updates on each section of Letter of
                Indemnity.</para>
              </entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="top">
                <para role="TEXT">Adhoc beneficiary addition is enabled in the
                following products: <itemizedlist>
                    <listitem>
                      <para>Import Letter of Credit</para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                      <para>Export Letter of Credit</para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                      <para>Undertaking Issued</para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                      <para>Shipping Guarantee</para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                      <para>Issued Standby Letter of Credit</para>
                    </listitem>
                  </itemizedlist>Refer beneficiary field of each product for
                detailed information.</para>
              </entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="top">
                <para><guimenu>Parent Transaction Information</guimenu> is
                added for Back to Back LC. For more details refer "<guimenu>Is
                this a back to back LC?</guimenu>" field in General Details of
                Import Letter of Credit.</para>
              </entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="top">
                <para>FCC auto-calculates the <guimenu>Increase/Decrease
                Amount</guimenu> fields when <guimenu>New LC Amount</guimenu>
                is entered and vice-versa. For more details refer
                <guimenu>Increase/Decrease Amount</guimenu> fields in the
                following products:<itemizedlist>
                    <listitem>
                      <para>Import Letter of Credit</para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                      <para>Export Letter of Credit</para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                      <para>Undertaking Issued</para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                      <para>Shipping Guarantee</para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                      <para>Issued Standby Letter of Credit</para>
                    </listitem>
                  </itemizedlist></para>
              </entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="top">
                <para role="TEXT">
                  <guilabel moreinfo="none">6.0.4.2</guilabel>
                </para>

                
              </entry>

              <entry valign="top">
                <para role="TEXT">The <ulink
                    url="FCC_modern_tradeservices_en.xml">
                    <xref linkend="CommonTradeFunctions"/>
                  </ulink>, lists the newly added features that are common for
                all the Trade products in Fusion Corporate Channels.</para>

                
              </entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable></para>
